00:30.781 --> 00:32.074
Uh, yes, I am.

00:32.158 --> 00:33.909
My man. Let's eat.

00:35.161 --> 00:38.539
Wow. Okay, now this is
called "Mazemen ramen."

00:38.622 --> 00:39.999
"Maze" means "to mix."

00:40.082 --> 00:41.083
- Right?
- All right.

00:41.167 --> 00:42.418
And the thing about this ramen

00:42.501 --> 00:44.253
is that it is
completely broth-less.

00:44.336 --> 00:45.796
So you really have to
take the chopsticks.

00:45.880 --> 00:47.590
- And really mix it up.
- I'm mixing.

00:47.673 --> 00:48.716
See how moist it gets?

00:48.799 --> 00:51.761
Twirling, Jeff, I think I got a
dangerously good bite coming up here.

00:51.844 --> 00:53.512
- Do you see this right here?
- Mmm, mmm.

00:53.596 --> 00:54.805
- I'm about to eat this.
- Eat it.

00:56.182 --> 00:57.850
Mmm!

00:57.933 --> 00:59.769
- Holy!
- Yeah.

00:59.852 --> 01:01.729
- See?
- That tasted so good.

01:01.812 --> 01:03.731
