29:48.704 --> 29:50.206
Nice to see you.

29:57.755 --> 30:00.549
Dude, I am so sorry about this.

30:00.633 --> 30:03.385
You know, you're gonna
be sad for a few weeks.

30:03.469 --> 30:04.845
Maybe a few months,

30:04.929 --> 30:07.097
but I promise you'll
get over this.

30:07.681 --> 30:09.892
I know,

30:09.975 --> 30:11.936
but I don't want to be sad.

30:12.061 --> 30:13.479
I want to be happy.

30:15.147 --> 30:17.483
I want to be really
happy with her.

30:17.566 --> 30:20.778
Yeah, but did you really
think this scenario through?

30:20.861 --> 30:22.696
I mean, what was gonna happen?

30:22.780 --> 30:25.282
She was gonna break up with Pino?
Move to New York?

30:25.366 --> 30:28.702
I mean, that's so much
pressure for both of you guys.

30:28.786 --> 30:31.080
I mean, she's lived in this
tiny village her whole life.

30:31.163 --> 30:33.082
She's been with one dude.

30:33.165 --> 30:37.461
Your relationship probably wasn't gonna be
this magical fantasy that's in your head.

30:37.545 --> 30:39.630
It was probably gonna
be a shit-show.

30:42.007 --> 30:43.676
I just thought we'd
figure it out.

30:47.930 --> 30:50.266
You know...

30:51.809 --> 30:54.895
I don't even know
if it's about her.

30:54.979 --> 30:57.022
I just--

30:57.106 --> 30:59.149
I miss that feeling.

30:59.233 --> 31:02.361
When we were together,
doing all that stuff...

31:05.072 --> 31:08.534
I felt really connected
to somebody.

31:08.617 --> 31:11.328
And it felt good.

31:14.415 --> 31:17.042
Now I just feel fucking alone.

31:17.126 --> 31:19.336
You know what you really
need is a distraction,

31:19.420 --> 31:21.297
something to get
your mind off this.

31:21.964 --> 31:24.008
So don't go home and look at

31:24.091 --> 31:26.010
old photos and videos of
us being happy together?

31:26.093 --> 31:28.387
I would stop doing
that immediately.

31:28.470 --> 31:29.972
But what I want you to do

31:30.055 --> 31:33.267
is go home, put on the
dumbest movie you can find,

31:33.350 --> 31:35.603
and watch that.

31:35.686 --> 31:37.438
That's...

31:37.521 --> 31:39.773
actually not a bad idea.

33:04.316 --> 33:06.068
- Okay.
- What are you doing?

33:06.151 --> 33:07.861
- We're gonna take a video.
- Okay.

33:07.945 --> 33:09.321
This is for, um, it's for

33:09.405 --> 33:10.698
Future Dev and Future Francesca.

33:10.781 --> 33:12.241
- Ah. Okay.
- Okay? Yeah?

33:12.324 --> 33:13.993
- Put it better, like...
- Okay, all right.

33:14.076 --> 33:15.661
...like, show
Washington Square Park.

33:15.744 --> 33:17.246
- That's good.
- Look at this.

33:17.329 --> 33:19.707
- Hello, future guys.
- Hi, how are you guys?

33:19.790 --> 33:22.418
Hope you're well. We just
wanted to make this video

33:22.501 --> 33:24.420
to remind you of the
really fun night we had.

33:24.503 --> 33:26.547
And I hope you guys are happy.

33:26.630 --> 33:30.884
Yeah. Maybe you're watching
this in different places

33:30.968 --> 33:32.636
or maybe you're together.
Who knows?

33:32.720 --> 33:33.554
Yeah.

33:33.637 --> 33:35.389
Whatever's going
on, hope you're happy.

33:35.472 --> 33:37.182
- Yes.
- Bye!

33:37.266 --> 33:38.559
Ciao.
